longTitle.p: to make provision for the relocation of Norwich Livestock Market; and for connected purposes.

formula.name: enactingText
formula.p: May it therefore please your Majesty that it may be enacted, and be it enacted, by the King’s Most Excellent Majesty, by and with the advice and consent of the Lords Spiritual and Temporal, and Commons, in this present Parliament assembled, and by the authority of the same, as follows:—
